th_Games_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games_England\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2006 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"Laugher\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"a decade\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"his junior\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hunt gave up on 10-metre platform diving, instead turning his attentions to the heady heights of cliff diving from 27 metres, winning a record 10 Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_Cliff_Diving_World_Series\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_Cliff_Diving_World_Series\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_Cliff_Diving_World_Series\"}, {\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Series\", \"score\": 0.9903181235960256, \"rank\": 0.0081290714980038, \"text\": \"World Series\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Series\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Series\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hunt\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"10-metre platform diving\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"his attentions\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"the heady heights\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"cliff diving\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"27 metres\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was during that time that he met his French wife, Sabine, eventually taking French nationality in 2018.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.833340846467734, \"rank\": 0.1972407070539565, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.833340846467734, \"rank\": 0.1972407070539565, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"Sabine\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His story then came full circle at the Aquatics Centre in Paris, as Hunt went up against Daley one last time, competing alongside Lois Szymczak in the men's synchronised 10m platform.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999889150787, \"rank\": 1.1084760824552965e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1572, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lois_Griffin\", \"score\": 0.9999999979722816, \"rank\": 2.027910488479991e-09, \"text\": \"Lois\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lois_Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lois_Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 1577, \"end\": 1585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryszard_Szymczak\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Szymczak\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryszard_Szymczak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryszard_Szymczak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His story\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"full circle\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"Hunt\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's synchronised 10m platform\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hunt said: \\\"It was so nice to have the Games here, close to England and in Paris.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6896569751326973, \"rank\": 0.42519950569621484, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999889150787, \"rank\": 1.1084760824552965e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hunt\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My wife is here, my stepdaughter is here, my sisters are here.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wife\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"my stepdaughter\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"my sisters\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's special for me having them come to this, my last 10-metre competition.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last 10-metre competition\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an amazing way to leave this sport.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an amazing way\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will continue with the 27 metres.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 27 metres\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But to be able to thank the crowd and finish on a nice dive was a special send-off.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice dive\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"a special send-off\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Watching Tom Daley and Jack Laugher come into the British Championships, there was one competition where they both beat me on platform when they were 11 and 12 years old.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.318755096495586e-55, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jack Laugher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the British Championships\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"one competition\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"platform\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in my 20s.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my 20s\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd rather quickly put 10-metre behind me.\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10-metre\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I saw this career ahead of me of 27 metres.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this career\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"27 metres\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For many years, I thought it would be impossible to go back to 10-metre.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"10-metre\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not even get to come to London 2012 to watch the Games because I had chicken pox.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.514506220085491e-13, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"chicken pox\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was stuck in quarantine with a bad internet connection.\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quarantine\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad internet connection\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really disappointed to see all my friends going and watching the event.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all my friends\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Little did I know, 12 years later, that I would get this opportunity.\\\"\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The differences between indoor platform diving and high dives from cliffs are enormous and so it was little surprise to see Hunt and Szymczak finish eighth of eight, in a final where Daley completed the full set of Olympic medals by taking silver alongside Noah Williams.\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2792, \"end\": 2800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryszard_Szymczak\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Szymczak\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryszard_Szymczak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryszard_Szymczak\"}, {\"begin\": 2916, \"end\": 2929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The differences\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"indoor platform diving\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"cliffs\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"little surprise\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"the full set\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2870}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medals\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were greeted to huge cheers with every dive, but so was adopted Frenchman Hunt, whose initial reason for returning to the pool was as much psychological as patriotic.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"huge cheers\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"every dive\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"Frenchman Hunt\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"whose initial reason\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained: \\\"I got the dual nationality in 2018 and we knew theOlympicswere coming to France at that point.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3193, \"end\": 3199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.980164494854961, \"rank\": 0.018752722332092613, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dual nationality\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicswere\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was at the end of 2017 when I had a twisting problem like Simone Biles.\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3276, \"end\": 3288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"a twisting problem\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was because of that, that I started doing 10-metre again.\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10-metre\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to dive but my twisting dives were becoming too much for me.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my twisting dives\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I decided to do 10-metre again.\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10-metre\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was thanks to that mental block that I got confidence enough to get back into 10-metre.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"that mental block\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3493}, {\"ngram\": \"10-metre\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now my wife is French, it just felt natural for me.\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then with Paris, the Olympics, that lit a lightbulb in my head.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3618, \"end\": 3623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999889150787, \"rank\": 1.1084760824552965e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3637}, {\"ngram\": \"a lightbulb\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe?\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe I can dust off the 10-metre dives.\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In my career, I have never been the best diver, but I loved it so much that I saw some of my friends eventually drop off and I just kept going.\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3734}, {\"ngram\": \"the best diver\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3768}, {\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, after 30 years of persistence and hard work, I got to have this opportunity.\\\"\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30 years\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3884}, {\"ngram\": \"persistence\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3899}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 3945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three decades from when he first took up the sport, and nearly two since a pair of kids got the better of him, a diver from Leeds finally got his Olympic moment.\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 4110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4073, \"end\": 4078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"score\": 0.5127792462112386, \"rank\": 0.8012848771124883, \"text\": \"Leeds\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 3999}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4028}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4036}, {\"ngram\": \"a diver\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic moment\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch every moment of the Olympic Games Paris 2024 live only ondiscovery+, the streaming home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4157}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4275, \"end\": 4286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedi